text: Generally killer Android is _very_ junior, but this one seems to have a bigger crowd than normal

That’s been my sense, but this one is hosted at not the Mossman’s house, so it looks like more people are going. I was chatting with some Crowd Compass people at a meetup a while back and heard that they left CC and went to eBay, so I bet they’ll host there more frequently.
